content.body:
### Shop 185/60R14 Tire Size
What kinds of vehicles are rolling on 185/60R14 tires? Think 90s and 2000s era Ford Escort, Honda Civic, Mazda2, Toyota Corolla, and Volkswagen Golf. For vehicles like this, you’ll probably want all-season tires that can offer good road manners, long wear, warranty coverage, year-round traction, a quiet, comfortable ride, and predictable handling. 

Looking for a new set of 185/60R14 tires? Check out the Falken Sincera SN250 A/S, General Altimax RT43, Hankook Kinergy ST (H735),[Firestone Champion Fuel Fighter](https://simpletire.com/brands/firestone-tires/champion-fuel-fighter), and Nexen N’Priz AH5 if you need a set of all-season tires that can delivery excellent year-round traction and performance.

Whether you drive a 90s to 2000s era Honda Civic, Toyota Corolla, or something else, SimpleTire has a set of 185/60R14 tires that meets your needs at a great price!
